Special Announcements






Marco Polo Residents

The entire Hawaiian Telcom ohana offers our deepest sympathies to those affected by the recent events at Marco Polo.  For Marco Polo residents who are Hawaiian Telcom customers, we’d like to offer support and assistance with regards to your Hawaiian Telcom service(s).  Please call us at 643-3456 (Residential) or 643-4411 (Business) and let us know how we can help; especially with replacing damaged equipment and/or call forwarding assistance. 


Bill Block Service
Hawaiian Telcom offers Bill Block service free of charge to prevent unauthorized, non-telecommunications charges on our business customer's bills. To sign-up, call 643-4411. 







